<h5> University of Edinburgh </h5> 
I was the instructor for <b>Math 3 - Introduction to Number Theory</b> where these <a href="writings/NumberTheoryNotes.pdf">lecture notes</a> were developed (with Chris Smyth and Andrew Ranicki)
